Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:02.05,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}《终空》前情提要\N{\fs40\b0}Previously on "Final Space"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:03.62,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞和奎恩共赴第一次约会\N{\fs40\b0}Gary and Quinn go on their first date
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:06.09,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}与此同时  地球正被缺口吸走  狗带啦！\N{\fs40\b0}while the Earth is being sucked up into the breach. Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:08.19,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞找到了反物质炸弹\N{\fs40\b0}Gary finds the anti-matter bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:09.79,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不过要想引爆它  他们必须先过了\N{\fs40\b0}But to detonate it, they're gonna have to get past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:11.80,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}总司令的火炉舰队关\N{\fs40\b0}the Lord Commander's fleet of incinerators.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:13.46,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他们能拯救世界吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Can they save the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:19.09,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}准备好收看《终空》本季最后一集史诗巨制吧！\N{\fs40\b0}Get ready for the epic season finale of "Final Space"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:40.22,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这些蠢蛋真的以为\N{\fs40\b0}Do these fools really think
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:43.22,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我会让他们合上缺口吗？\N{\fs40\b0}that I'll allow them to close the breach?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:47.29,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我是被泰坦选中的人\N{\fs40\b0}I was chosen by Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:49.30,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们可能过不了这一关了\N{\fs40\b0}We might not make it out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:52.63,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我只是想说... 我不知道我们是什么\N{\fs40\b0}I wanted to say... I don't know what we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:55.72,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}一队船员？感觉我们的关系比这个更复杂\N{\fs40\b0}A crew? Feels like we're more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:58.16,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}或许是朋友？但对我来说\N{\fs40\b0}I mean, friends maybe? But to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:02.24,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们更像是一个亲密  却又古怪的家庭\N{\fs40\b0}we've become like a close, but very strange family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:04.02,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果没有你们...\N{\fs40\b0}And without you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:07.04,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 我就不再是我了   - 我们！我们！\N{\fs40\b0}- I wouldn't be me. - Us! Us! Us! Us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:09.48,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 我们！   - 闭嘴  KVN！\N{\fs40\b0}- Uuuuus! - Shut the hell up, KVN!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:11.78,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我不会离开你的  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}I will never leave you, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:16.25,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我会做你永远的深空防精神错乱伴侣\N{\fs40\b0}I will be your deep space insanity avoidance forever companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:17.99,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我发誓  KVN！\N{\fs40\b0}I swear to God, KVN!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.02,0:01:21.26,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}无论如何  不管发生什么  不管我们去哪\N{\fs40\b0}Anyways, whatever happens, wherever we go,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:24.53,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}等这一切结束  我们一定要找到彼此\N{\fs40\b0}we find each other when this is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.26,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}就这样定了？\N{\fs40\b0}Deal?
