Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:05.53,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}太多战舰了  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}There are too many, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:06.87,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们不可能突围的\N{\fs40\b0}We'll never be able to break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:08.54,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE  你难道不能找一条路吗？\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E., can't you find a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:10.97,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们可以制造四级粒子灼烧\N{\fs40\b0}We can create a Level 4 Particle Burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:13.18,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好极了  不过鉴于我早就摆脱了化学试验材料包\N{\fs40\b0}Great. While I bust out my chemistry set,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:14.91,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}能不能给我解释一下你说的是啥？！\N{\fs40\b0}how about explaining what the hell that means?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:18.50,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}意思就是  我们把光折核心发射出去  然后引爆它\N{\fs40\b0}It means we eject our lightfold core and detonate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:19.35,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}什么？！\N{\fs40\b0}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:22.32,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你的好主意就是把光折引擎给炸了？！\N{\fs40\b0}Your great idea is to explode our lightfold engine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:24.05,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Ooo-whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:28.29,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE  准备发...\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E., eject the ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.33,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}已发射  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}Done, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.23,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}真的假的？\N{\fs40\b0}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.93,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}下次你能不能先警告我一下？\N{\fs40\b0}I mean, next time, can you warn me first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.20,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞... 不会再有“下次”了\N{\fs40\b0}Gary... there is no "next time."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:44.07,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}准备引爆  三... 二...\N{\fs40\b0}Detonating in 3... 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:45.51,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那是什么？\N{\fs40\b0}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.59,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}...起爆\N{\fs40\b0} ...Boomtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.69,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE 全速飞向缺口\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E., full speed toward the breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:07.10,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们有那么大一个东西需要合上\N{\fs40\b0}We got a freakin' hole to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.27,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这有意思吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Is this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:20.98,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}当然了！当然有意思！\N{\fs40\b0}It is! It is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:29.88,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}放虫群\N{\fs40\b0}Release the hives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.12,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}粉碎他们！\N{\fs40\b0}Crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.80,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}护盾已开启  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}Shields up, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:41.16,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE  那他喵的是啥？\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E., what the crap is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.60,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}是总司令的虫群战舰  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}The Lord Commander's hive ships, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.10,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果它们噬穿了护盾\N{\fs40\b0}If they eat through the shields,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:46.94,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们就没有其它防护措施了\N{\fs40\b0}there will be nothing left to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}护盾能撑多久？\N{\fs40\b0}How long will the shields hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.87,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}当前护盾完整度79%  数字正在下滑\N{\fs40\b0}Shield Integrity is at 79% and dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.41,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}至少还是... 还是个B-呢！\N{\fs40\b0}That's like a ... That's like a B-minus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.41,DESC,,0,0,0,,{\be15}B-对应百分制的80-82。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.14,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}还有救！\N{\fs40\b0}We're still good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.75,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}当前数据为63%\N{\fs40\b0}Now at 63%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:01.75,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}狗带！这个  这个撑死了只有D了！\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, crap! That's, like, a D, at best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:01.75,DESC,,0,0,0,,{\be15}D对应百分制的65-66。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.02,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}KVN  如果你不去外面的炮塔\N{\fs40\b0}KVN, if you don't get on the outside turret,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.29,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我就会把你打到只剩一口气\N{\fs40\b0}I will beat you within one inch of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:09.63,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}伙计们  我是最可抛弃的船员！恭喜我了\N{\fs40\b0}Guys, I'm the most expendable! Congratulations to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:12.20,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}月饼  你去干什么？\N{\fs40\b0}Mooncake, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.16,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Chookity pok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:18.29,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好吧  不过你不是可抛弃的\N{\fs40\b0}All right. But you're not expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.04,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  虫群在护盾上制造了太多缺口\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, the hives have breached the shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.78,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}KVN和月饼对付不了多久的\N{\fs40\b0}KVN and Mooncake won't be able to hold them off for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:32.98,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦不！哦不！\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, no! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:35.79,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这不是作战  这是死亡判决\N{\fs40\b0}This isn't a fight. It's a death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.22,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}鹰式机能击退虫群吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Can a Hawk punch through the hive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:39.86,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果冲力足够的话  可以\N{\fs40\b0}Provided there is sufficient force, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:42.93,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那我们就把反物质炸弹装在鹰式机上  然后飞出去\N{\fs40\b0}Then we will load the anti-matter bomb onto a Hawk and use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:45.13,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}但那些无人机看到鹰式机以后  会马上进攻的\N{\fs40\b0}But as soon as the drones see the Hawk, they'll destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:48.11,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}除非我们派一个人飞在前面开路\N{\fs40\b0}Not if we send somebody out first to clear the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.93,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 我来   - 这不是小孩能胜任的任务\N{\fs40\b0}- I'll do it. - This is no job for a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.94,0:04:54.87,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我面前的不再是小孩了  我面前的  是一个男猫汉\N{\fs40\b0}I don't see a kid anymore. I see a Man-Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:58.84,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 奎恩  我做得来   - 那我们就派小卡多开路\N{\fs40\b0}- Quinn, I can do this. - We will go with Little Cato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:00.74,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}所以他不会像他的父亲一样死掉\N{\fs40\b0}So that he doesn't die like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:03.88,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  太冷血了  抱歉\N{\fs40\b0}Whoops, that was insensitive. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.48,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}让我们为你骄傲\N{\fs40\b0}Make us proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.85,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE  给他一架鹰式机\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E., get him a Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:13.02,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 注意安全  男猫汉   - 别担心  我可以的\N{\fs40\b0}- Be careful out there, Man-Cat. - Don't worry. I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.62,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我太可以了\N{\fs40\b0}I so got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.63,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我太太太可以了\N{\fs40\b0}I got this so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:19.10,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  我可以的  我要出发了\N{\fs40\b0}Oooh, I got it. I'm gonna get this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.81,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好的  该走了\N{\fs40\b0}All right, it's ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.38,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好好想想  这是阻止地球被吸走的\N{\fs40\b0}To think, that's the only thing stopping the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:40.35,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}唯一武器  现在它就在我手里\N{\fs40\b0}from getting swallowed up. And it's all on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.05,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我还以为看上去会更酷的\N{\fs40\b0}I thought it would've looked much cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.49,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我应该画点火苗之类的吗？我带了好多笔\N{\fs40\b0}Should I draw some flames on it? I brought various tubes of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.56,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}住手！不要在上面画火苗好不好？！\N{\fs40\b0}No! How about you don't draw flames on the anti-matter bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:52.00,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}为时已晚了吗？正是\N{\fs40\b0}Is it too late?  It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:57.33,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 万一我做不到呢？   - 那就做到你的最好\N{\fs40\b0}- What if I can't do it? - Try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:00.00,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}万一我的最好都还不够好呢？\N{\fs40\b0}What if my best isn't good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:01.73,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你的最好  对我来说已经足够好了\N{\fs40\b0}It's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:06.37,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我有没有让你感觉更好了？当然！\N{\fs40\b0}Have I made things better? I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.07,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}该走了\N{\fs40\b0}It's go time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:11.35,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 你在干什么？   - 我在完成任务\N{\fs40\b0}- What are you doing? - Finishing the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:13.75,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不过我才是要把它带到缺口的人\N{\fs40\b0}Except I'm the one taking it to the breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:17.89,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 这是我的任务   - 真不巧  但这是我的命运\N{\fs40\b0}- It's my mission. - Too bad. It's my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.26,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你为什么要和我争这个？\N{\fs40\b0}Why are you fighting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:25.23,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}因为失去你  是我远远不能承受的事！\N{\fs40\b0}Because I can take anything, except losing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:29.10,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  天哪  为什么  奎恩？！为什么我们到了这一步？\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, God, why, Quinn?! Why are we in this situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:32.03,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}早在我发现引力干扰的时候\N{\fs40\b0}From the moment I discovered the gravitational disturbance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:34.17,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我就知道  这是我的人生大事\N{\fs40\b0}I knew this was my life's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:37.11,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果你真的喜欢我...\N{\fs40\b0}If you really have feelings for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:41.66,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 让我把这件事完成吧   - 我现在完全不知所措了！\N{\fs40\b0}- let me see this through to the end. - I am genuinely perplexed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:46.52,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}因为我... 我不想让你死啊\N{\fs40\b0}'Cause I'm ... I'm trying to stop you from dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.25,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}求你了\N{\fs40\b0}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.22,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那么  奎恩·厄尔冈\N{\fs40\b0}Then, Quinn Ergon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:55.66,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我会用尽最后一口气  确保你凯旋\N{\fs40\b0}I will use every last breath to make sure you succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:58.76,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这是个真实又纯粹的承诺\N{\fs40\b0}That's a real, raw promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.80,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 哈！   - 嗯\N{\fs40\b0}- Hwa! - Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.70,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}太他妈... 太他妈棒了！\N{\fs40\b0}Hell... Hell, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.40,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}等你回来  我们再继续\N{\fs40\b0}More of that when you come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.40,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不要离我而去\N{\fs40\b0}Don't die on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.14,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}真好玩  我还以为我会当那个英雄呢...\N{\fs40\b0}Funny, I thought I was gonna be the hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:13.68,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 不过你才是那个英雄   - 不  我们两个都是英雄\N{\fs40\b0}- but it's you. - No, it's both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:16.18,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们一直都是英雄\N{\fs40\b0}Always has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.44,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}给我开路  小子们！\N{\fs40\b0}Punch a hole for me, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:46.44,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好了  伙计们  全军出击\N{\fs40\b0}Okay, guys, all together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.82,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 谢了  小卡多   - 搞定它  奎恩\N{\fs40\b0}- Thanks, Little Cato. - Finish it, Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.96,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果有更多外援就好了\N{\fs40\b0}If only there was more help to call on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:02.76,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果有反抗军就好了\N{\fs40\b0}If only there was a Resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:06.70,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}等等  真的有反抗军  我还是领袖呢\N{\fs40\b0}Wait, there is a Resistance, and I'm its leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:09.70,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}反抗军？到了该反抗的时候了吗？到了！\N{\fs40\b0}Resistance? Is it time to resist? It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.24,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我是三烦·梅内德斯将军\N{\fs40\b0}This is General Tribore Menendez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:16.14,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}所有部队  去11区\N{\fs40\b0}All battalions to Sector 11. Reeeeorr!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Reeeeorr! Reeeeorr!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.21,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Reeeeorr!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:21.61,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Reeeeorr!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:25.12,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}虫群已渗透银河一号\N{\fs40\b0}The hives have infiltrated the Galaxy One.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:28.88,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}嘿！滚出我的飞船！\N{\fs40\b0}Hey! Get off my ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:31.39,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}啊啊啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Aaahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:49.21,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这就是死亡的滋味吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Is this what death feels like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.68,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不差嘛  只是  好奇怪啊\N{\fs40\b0}Not bad. It's just weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.41,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}正在接近\N{\fs40\b0}Closing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:59.82,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 啊！这只有我一个人了吗？   - 不  三烦还在\N{\fs40\b0}- Ah! Am I alone here? - No. Tribore's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:03.69,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我还带来了几个特别的朋友\N{\fs40\b0}And I brought some special friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.42,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:10.43,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}谢了  三烦  我正在接近缺口\N{\fs40\b0}Thanks, Tribore. I'm closing in on the breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:18.06,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不妙吧？这还用说吗！\N{\fs40\b0}Is this bad? It sure the hell is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:21.30,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不  三烦  我曾爱过你\N{\fs40\b0}No, Tribore. I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.94,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}现在谁来领导反抗军？\N{\fs40\b0}Who's leading the Resistance now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:27.64,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我来  我们要做的第一件事就是... 复仇\N{\fs40\b0}I am. First order of business ... revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.58,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}发射！\N{\fs40\b0}Eject!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:44.73,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}耶  一石二鸟！干得漂亮\N{\fs40\b0}Yes. Two at once! Nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:48.00,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}去死吧！走你！走你！走你\N{\fs40\b0}Down you go! Gotcha! Gotcha! Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.86,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哇！我真是太帅了\N{\fs40\b0}Wow! I'm impressed with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.64,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0} Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.94,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 嘿  盖瑞？   - 怎么了  KVN？\N{\fs40\b0}- Hey, Gary? - What is it, KVN?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:02.21,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 很好玩  对吧？   - 哦！KVN！\N{\fs40\b0}- It's been fun, right? - Oh! KVN!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:05.68,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我猜挺好玩的？嘿！我玩得很开心...\N{\fs40\b0}I guess? Hey! I had fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.65,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}太他妈美了\N{\fs40\b0}It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:16.83,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}召回虫群  准备好次元分流器\N{\fs40\b0}Call back the hives and ready the dimension splitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.14,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Chookity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.90,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Ooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.27,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}月饼！不！\N{\fs40\b0}Mooncake! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:36.65,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}啊！呃啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Ah! Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.69,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Ohhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.29,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Chookity pok!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:52.13,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你越挣扎  束缚就越强\N{\fs40\b0}The more you resist, the stronger the trap becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:54.66,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}嘿  月饼...\N{\fs40\b0}Hey, Mooncake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:59.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们可有的玩呢\N{\fs40\b0}We're going to have a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:01.88,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}正在接近缺口\N{\fs40\b0}Approaching breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:05.78,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}胜败在此一举\N{\fs40\b0}Here goes everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.35,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}呃！\N{\fs40\b0}Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:20.29,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.74,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}呃...\N{\fs40\b0}Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.51,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:42.18,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}呃啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Ughh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:45.65,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}汇报一下当前状态\N{\fs40\b0}Status report.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:50.39,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  银河一号沦陷了\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, we have lost the Galaxy One.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.89,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们还有左边的脉冲引擎呢\N{\fs40\b0}We still have a left pulse engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.59,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那是右边的脉冲引擎\N{\fs40\b0}It is the right pulse engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:56.93,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}而且  它不足以对付总司令了\N{\fs40\b0}and it is not enough to face the Lord Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:12:00.40,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  有一条你没考虑到的出路\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, there's one option you haven't considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.40,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你可以弃船\N{\fs40\b0}You can abandon ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:04.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我不会离开的  这次不会\N{\fs40\b0}I'm not running away. Not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:08.47,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这个想法曾经还说得通  不过... 我已经不是那个人了\N{\fs40\b0}At one point, that made sense, but... I'm not that guy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.07,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我会给你一块饼干的\N{\fs40\b0}I'd give you a cookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.08,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不过我猜  你已经长到不喜欢吃饼干的年龄了\N{\fs40\b0}But I think you've outgrown that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.84,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}什么？！不！给我块饼干！\N{\fs40\b0}What?! No! Give me a cookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.68,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我永远  永远不会抛弃饼干的！\N{\fs40\b0}I will never, ever outgrow a cookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:20.62,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}很抱歉  盖瑞  但它们不见了  全都不见了\N{\fs40\b0}I'm sorry, Gary, but they're gone. All gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.12,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}太糟了  HUE！\N{\fs40\b0}That sucks, H.U.E.!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.35,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}的确太糟了  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}It... really does, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:26.36,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们不能让那个人得胜\N{\fs40\b0}We can't let this guy win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:30.36,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  我见过这个表情  重新考虑  请一定重新考虑\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, I know that look. Reconsider. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:34.23,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}没门  我不会重新考虑的\N{\fs40\b0}No way, Jose. I won't reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:39.04,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  你设置了一条直接冲撞\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, you have set a collision course directly for
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.37,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}总司令的重型火炉舰的航线\N{\fs40\b0}the Lord Commander's Heavy Incinerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:45.11,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这是唯一能让他放过奎恩的办法\N{\fs40\b0}It's the only the way to stop him from taking out Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:46.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我还得去救月饼\N{\fs40\b0}And I have to save Mooncake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:49.65,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我非得给你开出一个清单吗？！\N{\fs40\b0}Do I really have to make a list for you right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.32,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}如果我们决定出去干了  就要干一场大的\N{\fs40\b0}If we're going out, we're going out big.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.98,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我同意  我们必须用尽全力\N{\fs40\b0}Agreed. We must do everything possible
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.79,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}毁灭那个混蛋\N{\fs40\b0}to destroy that dick loaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.72,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}咱们现在登场吧  你看如何？\N{\fs40\b0}What do you say we make an entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.26,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}就用它了  右侧的脉冲引擎\N{\fs40\b0}Right pulse engine is a go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:09.33,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}什么？他想干什么？！\N{\fs40\b0}What? What is he trying to accomplish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.20,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他已经失去所有东西了\N{\fs40\b0}He's already lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:17.01,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}迫近警告！迫近警告！\N{\fs40\b0}Proximity alert! Proximity alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:20.94,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}开火！把那艘飞船打飞！\N{\fs40\b0}Fire! Rip that ship from space!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:53.11,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我希望杀死你的过程能持续整整一辈子\N{\fs40\b0}I wish killing you could last a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:59.05,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 你准备好了吗？   - 动手啊！\N{\fs40\b0}- Ready for your turn? - Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:03.19,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:24.14,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  银河一号...\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, the Galaxy One...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.81,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}已经彻底毁坏了...\N{\fs40\b0}is destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.41,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE  快！把你的人工智能系统转到我的头盔里\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E., quick! Transfer your AI into my helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:32.52,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不  不  不  HUE！HUE？！\N{\fs40\b0}No, no, no. H.U.E.! H.U.E.?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.75,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}HUE！\N{\fs40\b0}H.U.E.!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:36.12,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}是  盖瑞  我在这\N{\fs40\b0}Yes, Gary. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.62,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我的老天哪  永远不要离开我  HUE\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, my gosh. Don't ever leave me, H.U.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:39.90,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}永远不会的  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}Wouldn't think of it, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:40.56,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Chookity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:56.91,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}终空次元分流器已装载完毕\N{\fs40\b0}Final Space Dimension Splitter has been armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:15:00.04,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}距离启动还有15秒\N{\fs40\b0}15 seconds until activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:06.65,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 月饼！   - 你在这啊...\N{\fs40\b0}- Mooncake! - Here he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:11.45,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}那个著名的英雄！“那个盖瑞”！\N{\fs40\b0}the infamous hero! The Gary!
